quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"Mulina lya Allah, Jwaukoto wejinji, Jwachanasa channope."
  1,2,"Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah, M'mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.",footnotes:318939:1
  1,3,"Jwaukoto wejinji, Jwachanasa channope."
  1,4,"Nsyene Lisiku Lyamalipilo."
  1,5,"Kwele Jikape tukwagalagatila, soni Kwele Jikape tukwaŵenda chikamuchisyo."
  1,6,"Tujongolelani kwitala lyagoloka.",footnotes:318946:1
  1,7,"Litala lya aŵala ŵanya ŵamwapele chindimba, ngaŵaga ŵaŵatumbililidwe (aŵala ŵaŵaimanyi yakuona nikuileka), kapena ŵaŵasokonechele (aŵala ŵaŵailesile yakuona ligongo lya ujinga ni kupotela).",footnotes:318949:1
